	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Most instructions affect only a subset of the flags, leaving the others untouched. The various documents should cover this. Clear all flags before every instruction only if you want an incorrect emulator. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


