		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">ens_leader wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Also, should I worry if both the Z and N bits are on after an instruction?</div>
<br />
<br />This should only be possible with BIT, PLP or RTI.  So if this is happening after LDA or ADC or something, yes, you have a problem.

		

